0.000Z","msg":"咁多老鼠聽到都打冷震  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4925f8d9ac5fe9b1b3cf00300b880646e06887","tid":792696,"uid":144466,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/024530_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F024530_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c8b4691e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f4fa4fc4008f4d3b85cf58ce4b98fe4a068865b","tid":792696,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1f0320c7738687e4d8024bbeb7f890c4381400d","tid":792696,"uid":128210,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"影響食安。<br />\n<br />\n篇文打法咁撚似支拿人，好中意節省一兩個字好似好撚威咁。<br />\n食物安全打晒出黎好似好難咁。篇文有字數限制？小學作文咩。<br />\n<br />\n支拿人又係中意省一兩個字咁。李總經理叫下叫下就李總。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:50:57.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4593e99ab2659bfb9256319ac846e872967b205","tid":792696,"uid":158645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"支那媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係啲懶係中性<br />\n專踩其他國家捧中國既垃圾"},{"pid":"3c668c242ec345851b21e92ba3442e7f00d93fd3","tid":792696,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4593e99ab2659bfb9256319ac846e872967b205","tid":792696,"uid":158645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"支那媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係啲懶係中性<br />\n專踩其他國家捧中國既垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"依篇文點捧中國法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時有睇開依個網國際嗰part，文化角力嗰忽有幾個都好鐘意寫日本，一個仲要係喺日本教大學嘅台灣人，你睇一篇就屌到人地個網垃圾真係好撚極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas